{"tid":2179822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大律師公會：《公安條例》中的暴動罪、非法集結容易被濫用。","createTime":"2020-08-29T11:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T11:53:16.000Z","uid":78519,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0e202c8c6cb2a59c395ddf1981f0d1b4ff49e2c3","tid":2179822,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T11:46:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/2GQ4POZE7BDNXG3OQVCSUCWB64/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2F2GQ4POZE7BDNXG3OQVCSUCWB64%2F&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5ZhvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=d1539dae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2F2GQ4POZE7BDNXG3OQVCSUCWB64%2F&h=fa358c8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/2GQ4POZE7BDNXG3OQVCSUCWB64/</a><br />\n<br />\n警方昨日就去年7.21元朗事件，以「暴動罪」拘捕13人，包括遭白衣人施襲受傷、曾報警並獲警方致謝舉報的民主黨立法會議員林卓廷。警方又否認當日為白衣人無差別襲擊，而是兩派人打鬥，形容「雙方勢均力敵、旗鼓相當」。針對法律問題，律師會前會長熊運信表示，兩幫人對打，一般很少以暴動罪控告；大律師公會執委石書銘則指，《公安條例》中的暴動罪、非法集結容易被濫用。"},{"pid":"ff8aac147da87e0d2d2aa783e2b6a0e106450039","tid":2179822,"uid":78519,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T11:47:03.000Z","msg":"大律師公會執委石書銘在同一節目指出，三人以上集結並作出擾亂秩序或侮辱性行為，令周遭人士有合理擔心這些人有意圖破壞社會安寧，即屬非法集結。但他指，要有人實際作出破壞社會安寧行為，現場才算是發生暴動。他指，兩派人對峙並動手打架，在法律原則下參與者都可被控暴動，舉例指，警方在遊行現場拉起封鎖線但有示威者推鐵馬要求開路，只要有警員認為有人擔心人身受傷害，都可以指控他干犯暴動罪，<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">認為暴動罪是很容易引用的指控，只視乎律政司和警方是否運用這個「大鐵鎚」，認為暴動罪被濫用的機會很大。</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e7713f099549e79e76228951174a7c683e43b3ed","tid":2179822,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff8aac147da87e0d2d2aa783e2b6a0e106450039","tid":2179822,"uid":78519,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T11:47:03.000Z","msg":"大律師公會執委石書銘在同一節目指出，三人以上集結並作出擾亂秩序或侮辱性行為，令周遭人士有合理擔心這些人有意圖破壞社會安寧，即屬非法集結。但他指，要有人實際作出破壞社會安寧行為，現場才算是發生暴動。他指，兩派人對峙並動手打架，在法律原則下參與者都可被控暴動，舉例指，警方在遊行現場拉起封鎖線但有示威者推鐵馬要求開路，只要有警員認為有人擔心人身受傷害，都可以指控他干犯暴動罪，<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">認為暴動罪是很容易引用的指控，只視乎律政司和警方是否運用這個「大鐵鎚」，認為暴動罪被濫用的機會很大。</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T11:47:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e66a9cd0f549c67bbf5ff8ef65c7663f5f05b2","tid":2179822,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T11:48:29.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"788e50d3a45318b286f5fb4ef3107870becd432a","tid":2179822,"uid":78519,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T11:52:11.000Z","msg":"好似有人放啲misinformation <br />\n大家應該將問題放返落法律粗疏嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n唔喺去亂屌人"},{"pid":"ee29bc4d6ae218e4b72d9624b8194c5463924e28","tid":2179822,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T11:53:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61e0dc98440f609dd8a20d173fac0d83e1f4b8dd","tid":2179822,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T11:53:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d19b67cc1656cedd5972661d8066963c7db2c8c","tid":2179822,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T11:54:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c673a8d31bf956313f4609453c7ade86db6d07b6","tid":2179822,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T11:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"h